{"tid":1453440,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］前線醫生秘方應對發夢後遺症!!","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:01:23.000Z","uid":48213,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2d38021d395dfbe927898ec77853efe9021e69","tid":1453440,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"有醫生朋友間唔時上前線，知道好多人發完夢可能呼吸困難同成身比火燒，叫我話大家聽點用秘方紓緩發夢後遺症，佢自己試過都有用。<br />\n<br />\n1. 用曼秀雷敦對付比火燒既感覺<br />\n<br />\n根據香港中毒諮詢中心最近既指引，催淚彈主要成份係chlorobenzalmalononitrile，又名CS催淚性毒氣，翻查文獻發現CS 會同一個叫TRPA1既痛覺感受器(nociceptor)發生反應，引致皮膚灼痛既感覺。胡椒噴霧有令一隻成分Oleoresin capsicum (OC)，但最後都係會trigger到TRPA1，而曼秀雷敦軟膏入面既menthol，可以抑制到TRPA1，暫時紓緩灼痛。<br />\n<br />\n建議大家用大量清水/生理鹽水清洗後，揸一層薄既係受影響既皮膚上面，記得係大量清洗之後，如果唔係殘留既化學物可以透過其他pathway去刺激你既痛覺神經，所以一定要大量清洗！！！<br />\n<br />\n2.用化痰橙粉同消災止痛藥對付肺部症狀<br />\n<br />\n橙粉(Flumicil)主要成分有NAC(N-acetyl cysteine)，雖然唔可以減輕症狀，但可以保護到個肺唔受更多傷害。呼吸困難同氣喘可能係肺炎(pneumonitis)引起，呢個時候用呼入性類固醇(哮喘病人會有，需醫生處方)或者NSAIDs(非類固醇消炎止痛藥)都可以幫到手。不過呢兩隻藥都有副作用，大家千祈千祈唔好自己買！就算有啲藥房有賣都千祈唔好！長期服用NSAIDs可引致胃潰瘍同腎衰竭，所以唔好長期食呀！<br />\n<br />\n當然無臨床實驗去証實以上既秘方，不過都係結合前線經驗同molecular level理論既建議，希望幫到大家。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqgHkDG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqgHkDG.jpg&h=7dff8d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhP52Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhP52Xo.jpg&h=96a55677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobHkJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobHkJb.jpg&h=00de3d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5096012/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5096012%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=cbdba11a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5096012/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xu0XT5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxu0XT5C.jpg&h=8e4cbaf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pA7jn9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpA7jn9e.jpg&h=d8b7b211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHc3PPh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHc3PPh.jpg&h=ac647015&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4886b808ace3c2cf82353691770d76ef6dc7a3f","tid":1453440,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"efc137486eef3a46de726be43fb9a245d0f4f5a7","tid":1453440,"uid":33885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ed9bcad2726193e870f3df7a0f9ea0e36a06509","tid":1453440,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"推，不過最好有其他醫護手足幫手fact check"},{"pid":"7df11ff379b1b2c9cf5e85ae45d947c2b9b23b78","tid":1453440,"uid":258288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9bd4194c7701e70646054944110952a98e733306","tid":1453440,"uid":47340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"開錯台喎師叔"},{"pid":"4d1da3c5e0abf1fc4f1da78745d665948b70f0b7","tid":1453440,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96cd431158baebb05119a3f97f517616b5f290fd","tid":1453440,"uid":34460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe77ac7d77fd9ce7708434a3c22a838e4ff13352","tid":1453440,"uid":224528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ed9bcad2726193e870f3df7a0f9ea0e36a06509","tid":1453440,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"推，不過最好有其他醫護手足幫手fact check"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"份野已經講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw push"},{"pid":"80eccf323aaf3b097b8e4734b655412ae8bce3ae","tid":1453440,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ad662546dbfc69fed833606faee5ec6e3ef8906","tid":1453440,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"24839c87be2f6e11818dd61ba51d5f1e9ecf2387","tid":1453440,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c52cd57fb5561b46587350e54b718cd477c2b2a3","tid":1453440,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ebc21ffc0184cfeb5e8e8110c4a9cf3f976e556","tid":1453440,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"輕pish 一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef87308b7f20369c85315052528a896bc1bd6b95","tid":1453440,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"睇錯前列線夢遺"},{"pid":"7b3f270671186b629fadcb2d1f6afb146fc0670a","tid":1453440,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"9c997205a9d88147edcd9e484ee74f4bc28cc55a","tid":1453440,"uid":48213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:28:44.000Z","msg":"Pish to hot door"},{"pid":"4ab2533cc76f3abdd9e653d3017740e289e71a77","tid":1453440,"uid":47340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a2f045afeb73b99399e3549c35a7b50405349b0a","tid":1453440,"uid":59363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"提提大家Flumicil買「保健品」會平過買「藥」<br />\n香港搵唔到就上iherbs 搵 NAC 啦"},{"pid":"5fda58f6fb24bb73e9668d8fbe65cdcb4dfe13a3","tid":1453440,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲第22日</span></span><br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通<br />\n無人落charge<br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6.疑似洗頭艇<br />\n（突發推上熱門）洗頭艇 被捕示威者被送到新屋嶺拘留中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446427</a><br />\n<br />\n香港811 back-up 影片 List<br />\n插贓嫁禍<br />\n太古近距離開槍 人踩人<br />\n警黑合作打記者 冇拉到人<br />\n示威者被打到頭破血流<br />\n黑警扮示威者做卧底<br />\n荃灣綠楊白衫打人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bc95337c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8</a>"},{"pid":"76fe12472ec0a8bd10f23be4eb49650add18a6c4","tid":1453440,"uid":174936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb810df3134c38a00800f63d2c7e3a19a7ef3f1","tid":1453440,"uid":258631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"95bbdec62bb93f942caafe43be2d3c27e344b755","tid":1453440,"uid":258631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"Fc"},{"pid":"2fc4cb3324aa9b32a1e60baa584a18d5f0132c9e","tid":1453440,"uid":122201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit